Gauge field components  are elements of the algebra 
(acting on the free module by left multiplication). In general, these
fields are time dependent. In this section we will search for 
static  solutions
of the field equations, in the gauge



Then, the static field equations have the usual form
[_i,[_i,_j]]=0.
The purpose of this section is to obtain solution generation
technique in the  gauge theory on NC cylinder, which will be 
analogous to the technique suggested in
Ref.  
for NC plane.

Let us first  recall how the solution generation technique works on NC
plane.
